{"tid":1659840,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"自動交BOT 上線喇 讓你HIGH 翻天","createTime":"2019-10-17T07:20:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-18T14:38:30.000Z","uid":216555,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"32f3c12ee713993d47907e88c947e836acac0cd2","tid":1659840,"uid":216555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T07:20:45.000Z","msg":"朋友在2014年寫嘅，冇伏。<br />\n呢個功能已經加入KKFly app，稍後教大家點用。<br />\n<br />\n手動轉：<br />\n&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n[TLDR] 自動交稅機下載：<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/PPSAutoTaxDownload\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2FPPSAutoTaxDownload&d=o%2BN67aGUGKsADGfJqajrgPaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=c27681da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/PPSAutoTaxDownload</a><br />\n　<br />\n&mdash;<br />\n　<br />\n前言：<br />\n&bull; 　呢隻 bot 係喺 2014 雨革時寫，當時只限自己及朋友圈自用，但最近連登又有人提起 $1 交稅，為免大家咁辛苦每日逐蚊交，不如貼出嚟畀大家用。<br />\n　<br />\n【公民抗命】教你如何合法交稅/差餉/水費交到政府蝕錢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1637669\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1637669</a><br />\n　<br />\n使用說明：<br />\n&bull;　請參閱 README 文件<br />\n　<br />\n常見問題：<br />\n&bull;　點解個 ICON 咁核突？點解仲用黃傘？<br />\n一個字：懶。2014年寫落唔想改。<br />\n　<br />\n&bull;　點解只得 Windows 版？我用 MAC 點算？<br />\n同上，無時間寫過其他版本，下載檔案內有軟件主要部份嘅源代碼 (Source Code)，有心人歡迎自行下載改寫其他版本。<br />\n　<br />\n&bull;　登入PPS後佢停咗喺某畫面唔再郁&hellip;<br />\n可能係軟件出錯，又可能係 PPS改咗嘢。如果再試一次都係唔得，就放棄啦。<br />\n　<br />\n&bull;　除咗交稅，可唔可以交其他錢？<br />\n基本上 PPS 交到錢嘅「商戶」你都可以用，詳情可以睇返連登個 post。但要留意軟件只會揀第一個「賬單類別」<br />\n　<br />\n&bull;　有無風險？<br />\n2014年仲有「不誠實取用電腦」，但2019年，條例已經廢咗，只要你係用你自己部電腦就唔犯法。PPS 及法例都無規定你唔可以手動不停咁交一蚊。至於黑警上門拉人，佢要拉，你無犯法佢都拉㗎啦，算鳩數啦。<br />\n　<br />\n&bull;　用 PPS 交其實同用支票交有無分別？<br />\n用支票交，佢要逐張入，當然比較麻煩。但問題係你開幾千張支票就算用印章都做到手軟。上網交可以全自動進行，所以方便啲。正常商戶每條 PPS 過數會被收取2蚊手續費，所以理論上你交嘅錢會全部變成手續費。<br />\n　<br />\n&bull;　有無毒 / 伏？<br />\n寫呢個軟件嘅時候一定無，但原作者我匿名放上網，唔會有 official website，因此會唔會有人改做病毒或malware再發佈就唔肯定。建議各位下載後自行掃毒，同時使用後更改你嘅PPS密碼，以確保安全。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cEauF9Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcEauF9Q.jpg&h=b1981072&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7adbd9ea25f755b0d1dd879b275ca45b2ef858e4","tid":1659840,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T07:21:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W04Z2Gp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW04Z2Gp.jpg&h=e79a1d2a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"cf4e54e31869e7b9b27c133d0542fa9b4dae9a20","tid":1659840,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T07:29:17.000Z","msg":"未dl，但我點數交左幾多？"},{"pid":"82f6f7fefcf4c370a3c6f02ada21beb07db5a3de","tid":1659840,"uid":261478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T07:36:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a349ee11f3a34cbb9df63153138e5cf70e413c78","tid":1659840,"uid":253418,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T08:23:10.000Z","msg":"其實政府蝕錢，咪揾小市民埋單，有乜著數?"},{"pid":"3fb9b88cea3aac358a0f4c14f3b4edd598c37a98","tid":1659840,"uid":216555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T11:10:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"84ed7ac11188dac116662baaec13c0d0e6d773a0","tid":1659840,"uid":6777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a349ee11f3a34cbb9df63153138e5cf70e413c78","tid":1659840,"uid":253418,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T08:23:10.000Z","msg":"其實政府蝕錢，咪揾小市民埋單，有乜著數?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T02:56:39.000Z","msg":"點埋單？唔通佢會加你稅？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12d48afb405cd4d35979da399272baf31261a332","tid":1659840,"uid":216555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T14:38:30.000Z","msg":"推"}]}